WEBVTT

00:07:59.410 --> 00:08:01.728
in a manner appropriate
to their cultural methods

00:08:01.752 --> 00:08:03.418
of teaching and learning.

00:08:04.101 --> 00:08:05.252
In 2007,

00:08:05.276 --> 00:08:06.926
when that was brought into effect,

00:08:06.950 --> 00:08:08.483
four countries voted against it.

00:08:08.507 --> 00:08:11.601
They were the United States,
New Zealand, Australia

00:08:11.625 --> 00:08:12.775
and Canada.

00:08:13.908 --> 00:08:15.724
Canada adopted the United Nations

00:08:15.748 --> 00:08:19.249
Declaration on the Rights
of Indigenous People in 2010.

00:08:19.273 --> 00:08:22.376
And in 2015, the government
promised to bring it into effect.

00:08:23.895 --> 00:08:27.776
So how are we collectively
going to respond?

00:08:29.490 --> 00:08:31.498
Here's the situation that we're in.